ouse Square Entered as secondclass mail matter at the postoffice at Rock ingham N C crs unaccounted for and 3000000 wounded whose deaths in li years have boon averaged at 10 per tout Morrison Inaugurated t With bands playing guns roaring and railroad whistles screaming at intervals Cameron Morrison was Wednesday at noon formally inaugurated as Governor of North Carolina The ceremonies were happily carried following level Attorney general j Qut in every detail ExLieut from 03000 to 4000 state auditor I QqV m3X Gardner presided at from 3000 to 4000 secretary of state 3500 to 4500 state treasurer An act was passed by the Legisla ture Tuesday raising the salaries of the constitutional officers to the DEMOCRATIC IN POLITICS I Correspondence from every sec I tion of the county inviled Phone i 182 your items SUBSCRIPTION RATES fWvear 200 Six months Three mcntas 125 75 i JOIJ WORK A SPKCIAITY j Ljovc FLc Truck iif vVfirfoaboro has ranee pro truck big machine ei days ago t r at"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-12T17:34:07.894Z", "group": ["ndnp/ncu", "university-of-north-carolina-chapel-hill-library-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn91068736/1921-01-13/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_elk_ver01:data:sn91068736:00296023188:1921011301:0104/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=406&w=270", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_elk_ver01:data:sn91068736:00296023188:1921011301:0104/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=812&w=540", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ncu/batch_ncu_elk_ver01/data/sn91068736/00296023188/1921011301/0104.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["richmond", "rockingham", "north carolina", "united states"], "location_city": ["rockingham"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["richmond"], "location_state": ["north carolina"